metadata.name: AquaPhoenix
metadata.description:
This collection "relics of yore" is filled with mystery, action and suspense. I use Greek and Renaissance art and mythology history to weave a cohesive story that keeps one wondering what is happening nowadays in the world.Im looking for a kind of bridge between the past and the present.
This collection of me is a combination of collage and painting.
size 4mg / 3960x5148px/
